Description: These bits are read as 0. The write value should be 0.

Bit name: Clock frequency setting bit when operating under group-A priority control
Description: 0: When operating under group-A priority control, frequency ratio between PCLK and ADCLK is 2:1 or 1:1. 1: When operating under group-A priority control, frequency ratio between PCLK and ADCLK is 4:1 or over.
